{"thag3.15:0.1":"Theragatha 3.15 ","thag3.15:0.2":"Tikanipata ","thag3.15:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag3.15:0.4":"Haritattheragatha ","thag3.15:1.1":"“Yo pubbe karaniyani, ","thag3.15:1.2":"paccha so katumicchati; ","thag3.15:1.3":"Sukha so dhamsate thana, ","thag3.15:1.4":"paccha ca manutappati. ","thag3.15:2.1":"Yanhi kayira tanhi vade, ","thag3.15:2.2":"yam na kayira na tam vade; ","thag3.15:2.3":"Akarontam bhasamanam, ","thag3.15:2.4":"parijananti pandita. ","thag3.15:3.1":"Susukham vata nibbanam, ","thag3.15:3.2":"sammasambuddhadesitam; ","thag3.15:3.3":"Asokam virajam khemam, ","thag3.15:3.4":"yattha dukkham nirujjhati”ti. ","thag3.15:3.5":"… Harito thero …. "}